1912:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * below the maximum system call interrupt priority.  FreeRTOS maintains a
1913:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * separate interrupt safe API to ensure interrupt entry is as fast and as
1914:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * simple as possible.  More information (albeit Cortex-M specific) is
