4507:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****         /*
4508:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * PLEASE NOTE:
4509:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          *
4510:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * This function is provided for convenience only, and is used by many
4511:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * of the demo applications.  Do not consider it to be part of the
4512:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * scheduler.
4513:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          *
4514:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * vTaskList() calls uxTaskGetSystemState(), then formats part of the
4515:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * uxTaskGetSystemState() output into a human readable table that
4516:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * displays task: names, states, priority, stack usage and task number.
4517:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * Stack usage specified as the number of unused StackType_t words stack can hold
4518:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * on top of stack - not the number of bytes.
4519:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          *
4520:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * vTaskList() has a dependency on the sprintf() C library function that
4521:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * might bloat the code size, use a lot of stack, and provide different
4522:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * results on different platforms.  An alternative, tiny, third party,
4523:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * and limited functionality implementation of sprintf() is provided in
4524:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * many of the FreeRTOS/Demo sub-directories in a file called
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccHprLhz.s 			page 81


4525:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * printf-stdarg.c (note printf-stdarg.c does not provide a full
4526:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * snprintf() implementation!).
4527:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          *
4528:Middlewares/FreeRTOS/source/tasks.c ****          * It is recommended that production systems call uxTaskGetSystemState()
